1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,751
An AI Agent's polished completion message is not proof.

2
00:00:03,701 --> 00:00:11,759
Reliable acceptance turns the intended result into a task, inspects the final state, and asks whether success repeats under fair conditions.

3
00:00:11,759 --> 00:00:15,567
First, define success before the AI Agent starts.

4
00:00:15,567 --> 00:00:19,278
Second, verify final state with the right grader mix.

5
00:00:19,278 --> 00:00:23,048
Third, repeat trials and audit the evaluation itself.

6
00:00:23,048 --> 00:00:32,365
Use the AI Agent Acceptance Sheet to record the outcome, setup, evidence, grader mix, reliability bar, evaluation gaps, and release decision.

7
00:00:32,365 --> 00:00:35,644
That is how “done” becomes a result you can trust.

8
00:00:35,644 --> 00:00:37,490
Follow Tiny Agent.

9
00:00:37,490 --> 00:00:40,528
Tiny Agent helps you get better at using AI.
